msgstr ""
"Ikona SMS na tipičnem obrazcu z informacijami o stiku v bazi podatkov Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/in_app_purchase.rst:67
msgid ""
"One way to utilize the *SMS* |IAP| service with Odoo is showcased in the "
"following steps:"
msgstr ""
"Eden od načinov uporabe storitve *SMS* |IAP| z Odoo je prikazan v naslednjih "
