msgid ""
"For **bar** and **line** charts, you can use the stacked option when you "
"have at least two groups, which then appear on top of each other instead of "
"next to each other."
msgstr ""
"Pri **stolpčnih** in **črtnih** grafikonih lahko uporabite možnost zlaganja, "
"če imate vsaj dve skupini, ki se nato prikažeta ena na drugi namesto druga "
"poleg druge."

